<br>
That's not to say I'm not open to the idea, I'd just like a little more feedback before I make a decision. I'm leaning towards &quot;not really needed&quot; right now. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=589241"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Chase</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
